definitions.definition: One of the small grains or drupelets which make up some kinds of fruit , as the blackberry , raspberry , etc.
One of the granular masses which constitute a racemose or compound gland , as the pancreas ; also, one of the saccular recesses in the lobules of a racemose gland.

main_definition: ( botany ) One of the small grains or drupelets which make up some kinds of fruit , as the blackberry , raspberry , etc.
